What's wrong, Mu?

188
00:12:08,500 --> 00:12:09,720
What's wrong, Mu?

189
00:12:11,040 --> 00:12:12,460
Y-you're not hurt, are you?

190
00:12:22,500 --> 00:12:23,590
Don't be afraid.

191
00:12:23,610 --> 00:12:24,490
Uncle's here.

192
00:12:24,640 --> 00:12:25,640
You're not hurt, right?

193
00:12:26,280 --> 00:12:26,920
Uncle.

194
00:12:26,920 --> 00:12:27,800
I'm so scared!

195
00:12:30,000 --> 00:12:31,020
Don't be afraid.

196
00:12:31,200 --> 00:12:32,160
Uncle's here.

197
00:12:33,490 --> 00:12:34,020
Let's go.

198
00:12:34,090 --> 00:12:35,080
Let's go back now.

199
00:12:40,640 --> 00:12:41,520
What's your name?

200
00:12:44,250 --> 00:12:46,230
Xiaoqi.

201
00:12:47,070 --> 00:12:48,910
What's your relationship with Master Wang?

202
00:12:51,550 --> 00:12:53,210
He's a distant uncle

203
00:12:53,890 --> 00:12:55,560
who raised me.

204
00:12:58,700 --> 00:13:00,040
Did he ever tell you

205
00:13:00,400 --> 00:13:01,440
why he let you enter the palace?

206
00:13:03,160 --> 00:13:04,000
Even if I die...

207
00:13:04,400 --> 00:13:08,040
Even if I die, I have to protect the prince.

208
00:13:08,440 --> 00:13:09,680
I have to listen to him.

209
00:13:22,070 --> 00:13:22,750
Xiaoqi.

210
00:13:23,080 --> 00:13:24,440
If you tell others

211
00:13:24,500 --> 00:13:25,630
what I am about to tell you,

212
00:13:25,650 --> 00:13:26,610
I might die.

213
00:13:28,950 --> 00:13:31,790
I... I won't tell anyone.

214
00:13:35,260 --> 00:13:36,430
When I was in Cloud City,

215
00:13:36,520 --> 00:13:38,180
I met with an accident.

216
00:13:38,350 --> 00:13:40,060
I can't hear anymore.

217
00:13:40,250 --> 00:13:41,520
From now on,

218
00:13:41,550 --> 00:13:43,370
you are my ears.

219
00:13:43,390 --> 00:13:44,640
You have to also teach me

220
00:13:44,710 --> 00:13:45,990
how to lip read in six months.

221
00:13:46,010 --> 00:13:46,850
Understand?

222
00:13:48,110 --> 00:13:49,070
Yes.

223
00:13:49,100 --> 00:13:49,980
Only two people

224
00:13:50,010 --> 00:13:51,400
knew about this secret.

225
00:13:51,560 --> 00:13:53,450
And that is only me and Master Wang.

226
00:13:53,700 --> 00:13:56,070
From now on, only two people will know as well.

227
00:13:56,170 --> 00:13:57,800
And that is you and me.

228
00:13:58,070 --> 00:13:59,970
A third person must never come to know about it.

229
00:14:00,090 --> 00:14:01,690
After Master Wang brought you in,

230
00:14:01,720 --> 00:14:02,330
he...

231
00:14:09,970 --> 00:14:10,740
Young Lord.

232
00:14:13,820 --> 00:14:14,850
How is it going?

233
00:14:15,030 --> 00:14:16,110
She's been locked up.

234
00:14:16,570 --> 00:14:18,740
But... what are you going to do with her?

235
00:14:19,130 --> 00:14:20,940
Are you really going to execute her?

236
00:14:22,870 --> 00:14:24,030
Have you ever had a cat?

237
00:14:26,050 --> 00:14:26,600
A cat?

238
00:14:28,490 --> 00:14:30,400
If you want a cat to listen to you,

239
00:14:30,720 --> 00:14:32,720
