247
00:14:49,180 --> 00:14:52,320
But... cats are not the same as humans too.

248
00:14:52,350 --> 00:14:53,070
Shut up.

249
00:14:54,360 --> 00:14:55,820
Lock her up for two days first.

250
00:14:56,140 --> 00:14:57,690
Come with me to her place tomorrow.

251
00:14:58,280 --> 00:14:58,840
Yes.

252
