263
00:15:35,440 --> 00:15:37,960
He said he will go to Melody Workshop with Young Lord tomorrow.

264
00:15:38,320 --> 00:15:39,650
I have to take this opportunity

265
00:15:39,760 --> 00:15:41,810
to plead for Fei in front of Young Lord.

266
00:15:42,480 --> 00:15:43,200
By the way,

267
00:15:43,570 --> 00:15:44,840
deal with this as before.

268
00:15:45,000 --> 00:15:47,520
Don't tell our parents until we resolve it,

269
00:15:47,880 --> 00:15:49,140
lest they worry.

270
00:15:51,110 --> 00:15:52,500
Lady Ruofei is naughty.

271
00:15:52,840 --> 00:15:55,640
She's getting more and more out of hand now.

272
00:15:57,160 --> 00:15:59,320
She's not afraid of implicating you, Sir or Madam.

273
00:15:59,320 --> 00:16:00,950
I am the one who spoilt her.

274
00:16:01,390 --> 00:16:03,870
It's time she learn to control her temper.

275
00:16:05,180 --> 00:16:06,060
You go first.

276
00:16:09,150 --> 00:16:10,790
[Su's Mansion]

277
00:16:15,480 --> 00:16:16,690
Don't be nervous, Mr. Su.

278
00:16:16,750 --> 00:16:17,360
Please sit.

279
00:16:23,290 --> 00:16:24,320
I'm here today

280
00:16:24,320 --> 00:16:26,510
to talk about how your daughter, Su Ruofei,

281
00:16:27,130 --> 00:16:28,480
