Assassinate?

284
00:16:33,030 --> 00:16:33,980
Assassinate?

285
00:16:36,720 --> 00:16:37,490
Young Lord.

286
00:16:42,560 --> 00:16:43,160
Young Lord.

287
00:16:44,360 --> 00:16:45,210
Young Lord.

288
00:16:46,280 --> 00:16:48,620
It's all my fault for not teaching her well.

289
00:16:49,320 --> 00:16:50,040
Young Lord,

290
00:16:50,400 --> 00:16:53,060
kill me if you want.

291
00:16:56,840 --> 00:16:57,790
Please rise, Mr. Su.

292
00:17:01,270 --> 00:17:03,180
Of course, I can choose not to kill her.

293
00:17:03,420 --> 00:17:04,870
But I have one condition.

294
00:17:06,200 --> 00:17:07,580
Young Lord, what is it?

295
00:17:07,730 --> 00:17:09,730
We will agree to any condition.

296
00:17:10,070 --> 00:17:13,060
I want Su Ruofei to be my private entertainer,

297
00:17:13,160 --> 00:17:14,920
and go back to Symphony City with me.

298
00:17:15,690 --> 00:17:19,240
S-So... she just needs to be an entertainer?

299
00:17:19,730 --> 00:17:21,280
Nothing else?

300
00:17:22,300 --> 00:17:24,030
What else do you want her to do?

301
00:17:26,720 --> 00:17:28,060
No problem.

302
00:17:28,120 --> 00:17:30,210
It's rare that you cherish her talent.

303
00:17:30,230 --> 00:17:32,030
That's her blessing.

304
00:17:32,170 --> 00:17:33,930
If we make this long journey to Symphony City,

305
00:17:33,950 --> 00:17:34,930
I can't guarantee

306
00:17:34,930 --> 00:17:36,510
when she will come back.

307
00:17:36,930 --> 00:17:38,080
Can you accept that?

308
00:17:39,680 --> 00:17:40,320
That...

309
00:17:47,270 --> 00:17:49,240
Birds that follow the phoenix will fly far.

310
00:17:49,600 --> 00:17:50,970
It is might not be a bad thing for Fei

311
00:17:50,970 --> 00:17:52,850
to follow you to Symphony City

312
00:17:53,200 --> 00:17:55,110
and get some training.

313
00:17:55,380 --> 00:17:57,870
Moreover, she has caused such trouble.

314
00:17:57,930 --> 00:18:01,250
It’s her luck that you chose to spare her.

315
00:18:01,530 --> 00:18:03,780
How can we not accept it?

316
00:18:05,180 --> 00:18:06,380
In that case,

317
00:18:06,990 --> 00:18:09,740
I have a few questions for you.

318
00:18:09,770 --> 00:18:10,650
Go ahead.

319
00:18:10,840 --> 00:18:13,570
Who taught Su Ruofei's music?

320
00:18:13,590 --> 00:18:14,580
Both my daughters

321
00:18:14,680 --> 00:18:16,320
picked up their skills at Melody Workshop.

322
00:18:16,920 --> 00:18:19,190
But Fei has her own ideas since young,

323
00:18:19,220 --> 00:18:20,590
and she wouldn't listen to me.

324
00:18:20,620 --> 00:18:22,850
She left after staying there for less than a year.

325
00:18:22,960 --> 00:18:25,530
She even abandoned the rank of Qingyin.

326
00:18:27,090 --> 00:18:29,740
Su Ruofei actually passed the Qingyin exam?

327
00:18:29,770 --> 00:18:31,510
Yes, when she was just 10 years old.

328
00:18:34,570 --> 00:18:36,130
She passed the exam at aged 10.

329
00:18:36,160 --> 00:18:38,760
My eldest daughter joined Melody Workshop afterwards,

330
00:18:39,080 --> 00:18:40,810
and stayed there ever since.

331
00:18:41,240 --> 00:18:44,500
Now, she has become the owner of Melody Workshop.

332
00:18:45,520 --> 00:18:48,110
Does Su Ruofei have any other hobbies

333
00:18:48,640 --> 00:18:49,900
besides music?

334
00:18:52,400 --> 00:18:53,080
No.

335
00:18:53,660 --> 00:18:55,150
She doesn't like staying at home.

336
00:18:55,170 --> 00:18:57,570
She always goes to the Green Flash Forest.

337
00:18:57,670 --> 00:19:00,310
She hasn't been home much these past two years.

338
00:19:00,650 --> 00:19:02,380
She has been focused on running her workshop.

339
00:19:02,800 --> 00:19:05,320
We tried to persuade her before.

340
00:19:05,430 --> 00:19:08,050
Later, we found that she really liked doing it,

341
00:19:08,360 --> 00:19:09,560
so we let her go.

342
00:19:14,620 --> 00:19:17,850
You said she's often at Green Flash Forest.

343
00:19:19,120 --> 00:19:20,120
Did she ever have

344
00:19:20,120 --> 00:19:21,480
any special encounters?

345
00:19:22,450 --> 00:19:23,920
Well...

346
00:19:30,920 --> 00:19:33,680
It seems that there's nothing strange

347
00:19:33,770 --> 00:19:35,720
about Su Ruofei.

348
00:19:42,380 --> 00:19:45,140
Then how come I can hear her music?

349
00:19:48,230 --> 00:19:49,870
Maybe God has opened his eyes,

350
00:19:50,200 --> 00:19:51,320
and sent someone to

351
00:19:51,350 --> 00:19:52,960
relieve you from the pain of your deafness?

352
00:19:56,000 --> 00:19:56,600
Young Lord,

353
00:19:58,260 --> 00:20:01,000
perhaps you can recover your hearing after listening

354
00:20:01,050 --> 00:20:02,320
to Su Ruofei perform for a few more days?

355
00:20:04,130 --> 00:20:05,650
That's possible.

356
00:20:07,560 --> 00:20:10,310
It seems that I have to keep her by my side.

357
00:20:14,170 --> 00:20:15,050
Then tell me

358
00:20:15,300 --> 00:20:17,310
why she doesn't want to be my private entertainer?

359
00:20:19,130 --> 00:20:20,240
I think...

360
00:20:20,530 --> 00:20:22,400
it's because she wants to run her own music workshop.

361
00:20:25,320 --> 00:20:26,400
She's scared.

362
00:20:27,790 --> 00:20:28,470
Scared?

363
00:20:29,880 --> 00:20:32,440
My brilliance must be too overwhelming.

364
00:20:32,520 --> 00:20:34,500
She must be afraid that if she stays by my side,

365
00:20:34,520 --> 00:20:36,360
she will be hurt by my brilliance.

366
00:20:41,170 --> 00:20:43,780
I... think there's another reason.

367
00:20:45,100 --> 00:20:46,550
Actually, she is

368
00:20:46,580 --> 00:20:47,900
not to blame for this matter too.

369
00:20:48,690 --> 00:20:49,710
I know.

370
00:20:49,730 --> 00:20:51,310
Even though you've been with me for so long,

371
00:20:51,580 --> 00:20:53,600
you still feel a lot of pressure.

372
00:20:54,760 --> 00:20:55,770
There's some pressure,

373
00:20:55,800 --> 00:20:56,490
but...

374
00:20:57,000 --> 00:20:57,960
Say no more.

375
00:20:57,990 --> 00:20:58,800
I understand.

376
00:21:00,370 --> 00:21:02,540
I think she should've figured it out.

377
00:21:02,570 --> 00:21:04,650
After all, it's her honor

378
00:21:04,680 --> 00:21:06,050
to stay by my side.

379
00:21:11,990 --> 00:21:17,200
[Clear Rivers and Calm Seas]

380
00:21:17,290 --> 00:21:20,340
[Melody Workshop]

381
00:21:35,250 --> 00:21:36,980
Greetings, Madam.

382
00:21:37,000 --> 00:21:39,610
Check every instrument and tune it again.

383
00:21:39,770 --> 00:21:41,610
I will personally tune the ancient instruments at Liuyin Pavilion

384
00:21:41,610 --> 00:21:44,010
before bringing it to the front of the hall.

385
00:21:44,410 --> 00:21:46,050
Young Lord will be here today.

386
00:21:46,080 --> 00:21:47,610
Do not make any mistakes.

387
00:21:48,280 --> 00:21:49,210
Yes.

388
00:21:52,250 --> 00:21:52,980
Madam.

389
00:21:53,630 --> 00:21:54,540
Is everything done?

390
00:21:54,590 --> 00:21:55,360
Madam,

391
00:21:55,380 --> 00:21:56,490
the music workshop has been closed,

392
00:21:56,520 --> 00:21:57,520
and everyone else has been driven away.

393
00:21:57,720 --> 00:21:59,280
All the valuable items of Lady Ruofei

394
00:21:59,320 --> 00:22:00,260
are all here.

395
00:22:09,790 --> 00:22:11,340
That is her treasure.

396
00:22:11,370 --> 00:22:12,730
If she knew you put it in here,

397
00:22:12,760 --> 00:22:13,680
she would be so angry.

398
00:22:13,780 --> 00:22:14,600
W-Well...

399
00:22:14,630 --> 00:22:15,830
Take it to Liuyin Pavilion.

400
00:22:15,950 --> 00:22:17,280
Ask someone to water it and take care of it.

401
00:22:17,750 --> 00:22:18,950
Yes, Madam.

402
00:22:21,970 --> 00:22:25,140
[Ninghui Hall]

403
00:22:26,320 --> 00:22:27,080
Let go of me!

404
00:22:27,690 --> 00:22:28,880
Where are you taking me?

405
00:22:30,320 --> 00:22:31,130
Where is Young Lord?

406
00:22:31,150 --> 00:22:32,150
I want to see him!

407
00:22:32,670 --> 00:22:34,210
I’m willing to be his entertainer.

408
00:22:34,210 --> 00:22:35,340
Let go of me!

409
00:22:35,340 --> 00:22:35,480
[Ninghui Hall]
Let go of me!

410
00:22:35,480 --> 00:22:36,040
[Ninghui Hall]

411
00:22:36,040 --> 00:22:37,610
I'm willing to be his entertainer!
[Ninghui Hall]

412
00:22:37,610 --> 00:22:38,440
[Ninghui Hall]

413
00:22:38,440 --> 00:22:39,210
Where is Young Lord?
[Ninghui Hall]

414
00:22:39,210 --> 00:22:39,870
[Ninghui Hall]

415
00:22:39,870 --> 00:22:40,290
Kneel!
[Ninghui Hall]

416
00:22:40,290 --> 00:22:40,570
Kneel!

417
00:22:43,030 --> 00:22:43,580
Young Lord,

418
00:22:43,740 --> 00:22:45,390
Criminal Su Ruofei is here.

419
00:22:45,560 --> 00:22:46,600
We can execute her now.

420
00:22:48,290 --> 00:22:49,080
Yes, carry on.

421
00:22:49,080 --> 00:22:49,680
Wait!

422
00:22:49,870 --> 00:22:50,650
Young Lord.

423
00:22:50,960 --> 00:22:52,260
Are you there?

424
00:22:52,340 --> 00:22:54,060
I'm willing to be your entertainer.

425
00:22:55,180 --> 00:22:56,500
If you want me to be your entertainer,

426
00:22:56,530 --> 00:22:57,920
that means you are my confidant.

427
00:22:58,790 --> 00:22:59,550
As the saying goes,

428
00:22:59,580 --> 00:23:01,030
a man dies for his confidant.

429
00:23:01,080 --> 00:23:02,320
Whether in life or death,

430
00:23:02,320 --> 00:23:03,720
I'll be your entertainer regardless.

431
00:23:03,740 --> 00:23:05,030
I'm committed to you.

432
00:23:05,250 --> 00:23:06,400
Did I hear it right?

433
00:23:07,280 --> 00:23:09,560
Boss Su is indeed sensible.

434
00:23:10,410 --> 00:23:12,320
Since you're willing to be my entertainer...

435
00:23:12,880 --> 00:23:13,550
Xiaoqi.

436
00:23:13,960 --> 00:23:15,810
Why don't we let her go?

437
00:23:16,110 --> 00:23:17,350
No, Young Lord.

438
00:23:17,560 --> 00:23:19,880
There might be a trap given this criminal's

439
00:23:20,240 --> 00:23:21,210
sudden change of attitude.

440
00:23:22,000 --> 00:23:23,120
Don't talk nonsense.

441
00:23:23,120 --> 00:23:24,120
I mean it!

442
00:23:25,170 --> 00:23:25,730
Young Lord.

443
00:23:25,840 --> 00:23:26,840
My sword is drawn.

444
00:23:26,960 --> 00:23:28,800
It's inauspicious if it doesn't see blood.

445
00:23:30,120 --> 00:23:31,840
What a difficult situation.

446
00:23:32,200 --> 00:23:33,880
One say she's sincere,

447
00:23:33,960 --> 00:23:35,690
and the other say it's bad luck.

448
00:23:36,620 --> 00:23:38,290
What should we do?

449
00:23:39,810 --> 00:23:41,060
How about...

450
00:23:42,560 --> 00:23:43,090
we execute her?

451
00:23:43,090 --> 00:23:43,720
No!

452
00:23:43,880 --> 00:23:44,440
Young Lord.

453
00:23:44,560 --> 00:23:45,980
If you dare to kill me,

454
00:23:46,040 --> 00:23:47,800
I'll complain to the King of Hell

455
00:23:47,840 --> 00:23:48,760
about you.

456
00:23:49,480 --> 00:23:51,400
How dare you threaten me?

457
00:23:51,870 --> 00:23:52,500
Xiaoqi.

458
00:23:52,770 --> 00:23:53,360
Execute her.

459
00:23:53,680 --> 00:23:54,240
Yes.

460
00:24:02,480 --> 00:24:07,650
[Ninghui Hall]

461
00:24:12,560 --> 00:24:13,930
How timid.

462
00:24:19,610 --> 00:24:20,290
Wake up.

463
00:24:26,910 --> 00:24:29,880
[Ninghui Hall]

464
00:24:35,330 --> 00:24:36,660
I'm not dead?

465
00:24:36,770 --> 00:24:37,530
What do you think?

466
00:24:42,560 --> 00:24:44,050
You lied to me.

467
00:24:44,210 --> 00:24:45,730
What do you mean?

468
00:24:46,190 --> 00:24:48,210
You tried to assassinate me once, and I lied to you once.

469
00:24:48,210 --> 00:24:49,330
We're even now.

470
00:24:49,850 --> 00:24:51,650
But remember what you just said.

471
00:24:51,680 --> 00:24:53,210
You'll be my entertainer.

472
00:24:54,140 --> 00:24:55,360
You lied to me just now.

473
00:24:55,400 --> 00:24:57,450
I won't be your entertainer anymore.

474
00:24:59,180 --> 00:25:01,480
That means you're fooling me.

475
00:25:01,890 --> 00:25:02,570
Xiaoqi.

476
00:25:02,730 --> 00:25:04,060
Execute her now.

477
00:25:04,240 --> 00:25:06,500
You're too much of a bully.

478
00:25:13,970 --> 00:25:14,650
Fine.

479
00:25:14,890 --> 00:25:17,270
I'll be your entertainer.

480
00:25:18,270 --> 00:25:21,360
But you should at least let me go home and say my goodbyes.

481
00:25:23,000 --> 00:25:23,880
Two hours.

482
00:25:23,900 --> 00:25:24,930
Go and hurry back.

483
00:25:26,850 --> 00:25:28,560
Two hours.

484
00:25:28,560 --> 00:25:29,920
Okay, no problem.

485
00:25:30,180 --> 00:25:32,430
I’ll be back on time.

486
00:25:39,410 --> 00:25:40,050
Young Lord.

487
00:25:41,710 --> 00:25:43,740
Her eyes are sparkling.

488
00:25:43,770 --> 00:25:44,770
She might be up to no good.

489
00:25:44,840 --> 00:25:46,600
Should I go and have a look?

490
00:25:47,990 --> 00:25:49,440
No one can refuse

491
00:25:49,670 --> 00:25:51,930
the offer to stay by my side.

492
00:25:52,180 --> 00:25:53,140
She is no exception.

493
00:25:54,330 --> 00:25:55,480
She will definitely come back.

494
00:25:57,590 --> 00:25:58,190
By the way,

495
00:25:58,550 --> 00:26:00,000
go to Melody Workshop with me.

496
00:26:00,730 --> 00:26:01,290
Yes.

497
00:26:01,370 --> 00:26:05,030
[Melody Workshop]

498
00:26:38,560 --> 00:26:40,600
Boss Su's fingers look so skilful.

499
00:26:40,700 --> 00:26:43,030
I am sure it sounds very beautiful.

500
00:26:43,540 --> 00:26:45,180
Unfortunately, I don’t have the chance to appreciate it.

501
00:26:49,700 --> 00:26:50,380
Young Lord?

502
00:26:57,860 --> 00:26:59,760
I'm Su Ruoshan, the boss of Melody Workshop.

503
00:26:59,760 --> 00:27:00,760
Greetings, Young Lord.

504
00:27:01,690 --> 00:27:02,930
I didn't know you were here,

505
00:27:02,930 --> 00:27:05,680
thus I failed to get the rest of Melody Workshop to come and greet you.

506
00:27:05,800 --> 00:27:07,210
Please forgive me.

507
00:27:07,850 --> 00:27:08,880
Boss Su, you are exaggerating.

508
00:27:08,900 --> 00:27:09,830
I am early.

509
00:27:11,220 --> 00:27:12,070
Young Lord,

510
00:27:12,090 --> 00:27:13,010
please come in.

511
00:27:13,160 --> 00:27:13,770
Okay.

512
00:27:30,000 --> 00:27:31,520
Please be careful, Young Lord.

513
00:27:31,610 --> 00:27:33,090
This jasper is very significant.

514
00:27:37,330 --> 00:27:39,160
Is this jasper yours?

515
00:27:40,130 --> 00:27:41,730
You recognize this, Young Lord?

516
00:27:43,150 --> 00:27:44,210
Did you share this japer

517
00:27:44,250 --> 00:27:46,130
with a young man many years back?

518
00:27:46,470 --> 00:27:48,100
You even saw the green flash together?

519
00:27:48,810 --> 00:27:49,890
You are...

520
00:27:51,480 --> 00:27:52,240
Shanshan!

521
00:27:53,390 --> 00:27:54,510
The mayor is here?

522
00:27:54,520 --> 00:27:55,330
Uncle?

523
00:28:03,290 --> 00:28:03,970
Shanshan?

524
00:28:04,740 --> 00:28:05,330
Shanshan!

525
00:28:06,250 --> 00:28:06,730
Mayor.

526
00:28:06,730 --> 00:28:07,290
Shanshan.

527
00:28:07,850 --> 00:28:08,290
Come and see

528
00:28:08,290 --> 00:28:09,450
what good stuff I've brought you.

529
00:28:09,450 --> 00:28:10,050
Jin.

530
00:28:10,050 --> 00:28:10,760
Hurry up.

531
00:28:14,330 --> 00:28:15,290
Mu, you're here.

532
00:28:16,240 --> 00:28:17,370
Greetings, Uncle.

533
00:28:17,660 --> 00:28:18,510
Good.

534
00:28:18,960 --> 00:28:19,520
Here.

535
00:28:20,840 --> 00:28:21,450
Open it.

536
00:28:26,200 --> 00:28:27,180
Look.

537
00:28:27,290 --> 00:28:28,810
Do you like this konghou?

538
00:28:30,750 --> 00:28:32,790
This konghou's craftsmanship is luxurious.

539
00:28:36,290 --> 00:28:37,290
The sound is crisp.

540
00:28:37,290 --> 00:28:38,330
It's definitely the best.

541
00:28:38,680 --> 00:28:39,290
I wonder where did you

542
00:28:39,290 --> 00:28:40,970
find such a good instrument?

543
00:28:41,290 --> 00:28:44,140
I thank you, Mayor, on behalf of Melody Workshop's musicians.

544
00:28:44,330 --> 00:28:45,860
Why are you thanking on their behalf?

545
00:28:46,250 --> 00:28:47,210
I asked

546
00:28:47,330 --> 00:28:49,730
the Manufacturing Bureau at Symphony City to make

547
00:28:49,730 --> 00:28:51,050
this konghou specially for you.

548
00:28:51,400 --> 00:28:52,360
For me?

549
00:28:53,970 --> 00:28:55,730
Isn't Mu going to select a musician?

550
00:28:55,880 --> 00:28:57,030
Use this then.

551
00:28:57,210 --> 00:28:58,120
I'm sure you'll win.

552
00:28:59,030 --> 00:29:00,230
Thank you for your kindness, Mayor.

553
00:29:00,530 --> 00:29:01,120
But...

554
00:29:01,140 --> 00:29:02,190
No but's.

555
00:29:02,220 --> 00:29:02,940
Just take it.

556
00:29:04,790 --> 00:29:05,510
By the way, Mu,

557
00:29:05,890 --> 00:29:08,140
have you read my brother's order?

558
00:29:08,400 --> 00:29:09,410
You'd yet to arrive.

559
00:29:09,430 --> 00:29:10,910
How dare I announce it without permission?

560
00:29:11,800 --> 00:29:12,350
Okay.

561
00:29:12,460 --> 00:29:13,540
Let's get down to business.

562
00:29:13,880 --> 00:29:14,390
Okay.

563
00:29:16,730 --> 00:29:19,250
If you are selected as the winning musician of Melody Workshop,

564
00:29:19,370 --> 00:29:20,960
you'll earn the golden ribbon,

565
00:29:21,040 --> 00:29:22,920
and be qualified to enter Symphony Workshop,

566
00:29:23,560 --> 00:29:26,290
and return to Symphony City with me.

567
00:29:26,810 --> 00:29:28,570
The winner of the Symphony Workshop competition

568
00:29:28,610 --> 00:29:30,380
will play a song at for Madam Yaoshan

569
00:29:30,490 --> 00:29:33,370
at Jiuru Banquet,

570
00:29:33,450 --> 00:29:36,380
and earn the title of the new music minister.

571
00:29:37,250 --> 00:29:38,490
Great!

572
00:29:39,560 --> 00:29:40,470
All right.

573
00:29:41,030 --> 00:29:42,480
You know the rules.

574
00:29:42,700 --> 00:29:43,890
Go and prepare for the competition

575
00:29:43,890 --> 00:29:45,090
happening three days later.

576
00:29:45,260 --> 00:29:45,840
Yes.

577
00:29:45,860 --> 00:29:46,540
Yes.

578
00:29:47,160 --> 00:29:47,830
Shanshan.

579
00:29:48,450 --> 00:29:49,360
Uncle.

580
00:29:50,900 --> 00:29:52,280
I heard you ordered

581
00:29:52,320 --> 00:29:54,760
to close down all of Cloud City's private workshops.

582
00:29:56,360 --> 00:29:56,960
Yes.

583
00:29:57,400 --> 00:29:58,880
How good can those people be?

584
00:29:59,120 --> 00:30:00,640
But Father ordered

585
00:30:00,660 --> 00:30:02,740
to choose the best musicians of Dongsheng.

586
00:30:03,130 --> 00:30:05,300
If we only choose from the official workshop,

587
00:30:05,500 --> 00:30:06,460
the people would think

588
00:30:06,490 --> 00:30:07,930
we're being unfair.

589
00:30:08,360 --> 00:30:09,910
What about being unfair?

590
00:30:10,530 --> 00:30:12,570
Those people in the private workshops are all thugs.

591
00:30:12,570 --> 00:30:13,810
What's there to hear?

592
00:30:14,200 --> 00:30:15,250
Besides,

593
00:30:15,270 --> 00:30:17,150
we own Symphony Workshop.

594
00:30:17,150 --> 00:30:18,090
We have the final say

595
00:30:18,090 --> 00:30:19,230
on what the rules will be.

596
00:30:19,230 --> 00:30:20,090
Uncle.

597
00:30:20,290 --> 00:30:20,840
Enough.

598
00:30:24,030 --> 00:30:24,930
Boss Su.

599
00:30:25,690 --> 00:30:26,520
Yes.

600
00:30:26,770 --> 00:30:28,120
Would you be willing to

601
00:30:28,120 --> 00:30:30,170
compete with the musicians from private workshops,

602
00:30:30,290 --> 00:30:31,680
and have a fair fight for the championship?

603
00:30:33,330 --> 00:30:34,330
I'm willing to.

604
00:30:34,460 --> 00:30:35,540
Shanshan.

605
00:30:35,730 --> 00:30:36,490
Mayor.

606
00:30:36,510 --> 00:30:38,320
Do you not trust my abilities?

607
00:30:39,360 --> 00:30:41,210
Of course I trust you.

608
00:30:42,310 --> 00:30:43,240
I just can't bear to

609
00:30:43,240 --> 00:30:44,730
let you waste so much effort.

610
00:30:45,490 --> 00:30:46,730
Thank you, Mayor.

611
00:30:47,080 --> 00:30:48,080
But I, Ruoshan,

612
00:30:48,370 --> 00:30:50,280
wants to compete fairly and squarely.

613
00:30:51,850 --> 00:30:52,680
Uncle, look.

614
00:30:53,130 --> 00:30:54,970
Please give the order then.

615
00:30:55,210 --> 00:30:58,570
Private workshops and Melody Workshop will compete

616
00:30:58,600 --> 00:30:59,360
in three days.

617
00:31:01,280 --> 00:31:01,840
Xiaoqi.

618
00:31:03,970 --> 00:31:04,920
This golden ribbon

619
00:31:04,920 --> 00:31:07,170
will be temporarily kept by Melody Workshop.

620
00:31:07,930 --> 00:31:08,570
Yes.

621
00:31:21,440 --> 00:31:23,600
[Liuyin Pavilion]

622
00:31:28,650 --> 00:31:30,820
I didn't expect you to have such an encounter.

623
00:31:30,930 --> 00:31:33,110
I thought the green flash was just a legend.

624
00:31:33,290 --> 00:31:34,370
Turns out, it's true.

625
00:31:34,370 --> 00:31:35,050
Yes.

626
00:31:35,050 --> 00:31:37,210
And the green flash is just like the legend.

627
00:31:37,210 --> 00:31:38,610
It can cure people.

628
00:31:38,770 --> 00:31:41,440
That boy had already vomited blood and fainted.

629
00:31:41,440 --> 00:31:42,970
but he woke up immediately

630
00:31:42,970 --> 00:31:44,750
after the green flash shone on him.

631
00:31:45,050 --> 00:31:46,450
No wonder so many sick people

632
00:31:46,450 --> 00:31:47,970
would head towards Green Flash Forest.

633
00:31:48,090 --> 00:31:49,570
They must want to see the green flash.

634
00:31:49,770 --> 00:31:51,880
I guess there's something magical about the green flash.

635
00:31:52,050 --> 00:31:53,880
If you see it, you will reap a miracle.

636
00:31:56,330 --> 00:31:57,730
Then this is called...

637
00:31:58,130 --> 00:31:58,890
Jasper.

638
00:31:58,890 --> 00:32:00,130
I named it.

639
00:32:00,610 --> 00:32:01,530
Did this jasper

640
00:32:01,530 --> 00:32:03,810
grow after the green flash disappeared?

641
00:32:04,090 --> 00:32:04,810
Yes.

642
00:32:04,880 --> 00:32:06,570
So I think this jasper

643
00:32:06,570 --> 00:32:08,570
has something to do with the green flash.

644
00:32:09,100 --> 00:32:10,370
But that petty chap

645
00:32:10,370 --> 00:32:11,890
wanted to take the bigger half.

646
00:32:12,400 --> 00:32:13,840
I saw that he was injured,

647
00:32:13,860 --> 00:32:15,180
so I gave it to him.

648
00:32:15,200 --> 00:32:16,690
You're so kind.

649
00:32:16,760 --> 00:32:18,840
What happened to that boy?

650
00:32:19,780 --> 00:32:21,700
He should have gone home.

651
00:32:21,720 --> 00:32:23,320
He doesn't seem to be a person of Cloud City.

652
00:32:23,520 --> 00:32:24,910
But we had a deal.

653
00:32:24,940 --> 00:32:26,650
If he comes to Cloud City again,

654
00:32:26,820 --> 00:32:29,880
we'll use this jasper to recognize each other.

655
00:32:37,470 --> 00:32:38,580
Boss Su.

656
00:32:44,270 --> 00:32:44,970
Boss Su.

657
00:32:45,150 --> 00:32:45,890
Young Lord.

658
00:32:46,120 --> 00:32:47,080
Can I come in?

659
00:32:47,780 --> 00:32:48,620
Please come in.

660
00:32:52,490 --> 00:32:54,050
Mayor didn't come with you?

661
00:32:55,090 --> 00:32:56,650
Uncle has something to do at home,

662
00:32:56,670 --> 00:32:57,720
so he went back first.

663
00:33:00,430 --> 00:33:01,200
I came here

664
00:33:01,200 --> 00:33:02,890
to finish what I didn't manage to say.

665
00:33:04,370 --> 00:33:06,050
I was just about to ask you too.

666
00:33:06,540 --> 00:33:07,930
This jasper is an extremely private matter.

667
00:33:08,030 --> 00:33:09,800
How did you know?

668
00:33:24,210 --> 00:33:26,920
You said it’s private matter.

669
00:33:27,490 --> 00:33:28,810
If I hadn't experienced it,

670
00:33:29,060 --> 00:33:30,310
how would I know?

671
00:33:33,090 --> 00:33:35,210
Are you the petty chap

672
00:33:35,210 --> 00:33:38,210
who took the bigger half of the jasper away?

673
00:33:39,120 --> 00:33:40,280
Petty chap?

674
00:33:41,410 --> 00:33:42,360
I'm sorry.

675
00:33:45,370 --> 00:33:47,130
I was too willful back then,

676
00:33:47,160 --> 00:33:48,640
and took the bigger half away.

677
00:33:49,180 --> 00:33:50,780
Even if you call me a petty chap,

678
00:33:51,030 --> 00:33:52,790
there's really nothing wrong with that.

679
00:33:54,600 --> 00:33:55,810
We promised

680
00:33:56,050 --> 00:33:57,690
to meet each other again with this jasper.

681
00:33:58,300 --> 00:33:59,860
I've lived up to my promise.

682
00:34:02,940 --> 00:34:05,220
I didn’t know who you were back then.

683
00:34:05,240 --> 00:34:06,570
Please forgive me

684
00:34:06,630 --> 00:34:07,900
if I had been rude.

685
00:34:19,610 --> 00:34:20,400
Open it.

686
00:34:26,040 --> 00:34:27,330
This time,

687
00:34:27,370 --> 00:34:29,450
besides choosing musicians for my father,

688
00:34:30,080 --> 00:34:31,080
I also came to Cloud City to look for you.

689
00:34:31,570 --> 00:34:32,860
I got someone to carefully make

690
00:34:32,890 --> 00:34:35,100
this jade brooch

691
00:34:35,130 --> 00:34:36,600
after leaving Green Flash Forest.

692
00:34:37,100 --> 00:34:38,580
I kept it with me for many years,

693
00:34:39,020 --> 00:34:41,010
with hopes that when we meet again,

694
00:34:41,280 --> 00:34:42,560
I can personally give it to you.

695
00:34:43,620 --> 00:34:45,410
Since you're going to take part in the audition,

696
00:34:45,450 --> 00:34:47,570
I hope you will be the one

697
00:34:47,750 --> 00:34:48,790
that follows me back to Symphony City.

698
00:34:49,580 --> 00:34:51,620
I, Ruoshan, will not let you down, Young Lord.

699
00:34:53,210 --> 00:34:54,240
Young Lord,

700
00:34:55,010 --> 00:34:56,640
I have a favor to ask you.

701
00:34:57,550 --> 00:34:58,150
Sure.

702
00:34:58,170 --> 00:34:59,090
Go ahead.

703
00:35:00,160 --> 00:35:02,490
My sister accidentally offended you yesterday,

704
00:35:02,570 --> 00:35:04,080
and committed the crime of disrespect.

705
00:35:04,580 --> 00:35:06,610
Please forgive her this time,

706
00:35:06,630 --> 00:35:07,800
seeing that she didn't mean it.

707
00:35:17,930 --> 00:35:20,080
She tried to assassinate me.

708
00:35:20,110 --> 00:35:21,870
That's a crime punishable by execution.

709
00:35:23,920 --> 00:35:24,440
Well...

710
00:35:26,680 --> 00:35:28,080
But seeing that Su Ruofei

711
00:35:28,110 --> 00:35:29,560
is your younger sister,

712
00:35:29,810 --> 00:35:31,490
I can spare her life.

713
00:35:33,090 --> 00:35:34,470
She can be pardoned,

714
00:35:34,730 --> 00:35:35,920
but she can't escape punishment.

715
00:35:36,720 --> 00:35:37,440
Forget it.

716
00:35:38,120 --> 00:35:39,850
I ask that she stay by my side,

717
00:35:39,950 --> 00:35:42,030
and be my private entertainer to atone for her sins.

718
00:35:42,680 --> 00:35:44,000
Private entertainer?

719
00:35:46,410 --> 00:35:47,620
But don't worry, Boss Su.

720
00:35:47,710 --> 00:35:48,990
I won't give her a hard time.

721
00:35:50,250 --> 00:35:52,150
Thank you for your benevolence.

722
00:35:52,350 --> 00:35:53,750
It's a blessing in diguise for Fei

723
00:35:53,780 --> 00:35:55,370
to be able to by your side.

724
00:35:56,900 --> 00:35:59,660
But how long will she be your

725
00:35:59,690 --> 00:36:00,770
private entertainer for?

726
00:36:01,640 --> 00:36:04,420
That depends on her performance.

727
00:36:05,960 --> 00:36:08,010
Why does Young Lord want to bring Fei back to Symphony City?

728
00:36:12,750 --> 00:36:14,530
It seems that I have to work harder in order to

729
00:36:14,530 --> 00:36:15,610
enter Symphony Workshop.

730
00:36:15,720 --> 00:36:17,840
In that way, I can take care of Fei

731
00:36:17,840 --> 00:36:19,410
when we're at Symphony City.

732
00:36:20,310 --> 00:36:21,310
I'm sure you will do well.

733
00:36:28,350 --> 00:36:29,310
We found her.

734
00:36:30,240 --> 00:36:31,640
She really didn't go home.

735
00:36:31,660 --> 00:36:32,420
Just as I guessed,

736
00:36:32,450 --> 00:36:33,450
she was up to no good.

737
00:36:34,540 --> 00:36:35,710
She really ran away?

738
00:36:36,570 --> 00:36:39,280
I didn't realise she had such an inferiority complex.

739
00:36:39,740 --> 00:36:41,470
She's so afraid to stay by my side.

740
00:36:45,530 --> 00:36:46,080
Young Lord,

741
00:36:46,330 --> 00:36:49,440
I don’t think it’s about her inferiority complex.

742
00:36:49,510 --> 00:36:51,800
If not, what else could it be?

743
00:36:52,790 --> 00:36:53,530
How about this?

744
00:36:53,970 --> 00:36:55,290
Go to my uncle

745
00:36:55,310 --> 00:36:56,760
and ask him to issue a warrant.

746
00:36:56,790 --> 00:36:57,710
Let's find her first.

747
00:36:58,280 --> 00:37:00,280
Maybe if Su Ruofei had seen it,

748
00:37:00,370 --> 00:37:02,160
she would run back in fear.

749
00:37:03,960 --> 00:37:04,670
Young Lord,

750
00:37:05,410 --> 00:37:06,360
I think

751
00:37:07,240 --> 00:37:09,560
even if Su Ruofei comes back,

752
00:37:10,180 --> 00:37:12,280
she also wouldn't listen to you well.

753
00:37:13,410 --> 00:37:16,200
It's only interesting if she's disobedient.

754
00:37:40,350 --> 00:37:42,800
It was quite pleasant to sleep deep in the forest

755
00:37:42,800 --> 00:37:44,170
and under the stars at night.

756
00:37:46,520 --> 00:37:50,340
But Young Lord wouldn’t help me.

757
00:37:50,730 --> 00:37:51,250
No.

758
00:37:51,590 --> 00:37:53,270
I have to think of another way.

759
00:37:59,460 --> 00:38:01,510
Let's eat first.

760
00:38:07,370 --> 00:38:08,290
What does it say?

761
00:38:08,410 --> 00:38:09,130
Wanted?

762
00:38:09,890 --> 00:38:11,120
Su Ruofei.

763
00:38:11,570 --> 00:38:12,680
The workshop?

764
00:38:14,250 --> 00:38:15,410
The boss of Green Flash Workshop?

765
00:38:15,430 --> 00:38:16,520
Yes, yes.

766
00:38:16,580 --> 00:38:17,170
It's her.

767
00:38:17,170 --> 00:38:20,810
The boss of Green Flash Workshop, Su Ruofei

768
00:38:21,060 --> 00:38:26,610
has escaped from her attempt at assassinating Lord of Leisure.

769
00:38:31,720 --> 00:38:35,880
Young Lord actually put out an arrest warrant for me?

770
00:38:37,790 --> 00:38:40,940
I thought I would be fine after hiding for two days.

771
00:38:41,560 --> 00:38:43,220
