772
00:38:43,280 --> 00:38:46,250
Reward of 50?

773
00:38:47,860 --> 00:38:49,190
[Reward of 10,000 taels of silver]

774
00:38:51,040 --> 00:38:52,890
That's a big difference.

775
00:38:52,890 --> 00:38:54,370
I'm that worthless?

776
00:38:57,970 --> 00:38:59,050
That's a serious crime.

777
00:38:59,050 --> 00:39:00,410
Have you seen this person?

778
00:39:00,530 --> 00:39:01,410
No.

779
00:39:01,850 --> 00:39:02,490
What about you?

780
00:39:02,650 --> 00:39:04,210
No. Let's try.

781
00:39:04,490 --> 00:39:05,200
Soldiers?

782
00:39:06,490 --> 00:39:07,530
Yes, sir. Let's go.

783
00:39:51,450 --> 00:39:53,920
[Wanted]

784
00:40:05,590 --> 00:40:06,240
Bro.

785
00:40:06,350 --> 00:40:07,200
Could we share a table?

786
00:40:14,230 --> 00:40:15,080
Don't worry.

787
00:40:15,110 --> 00:40:16,520
I'm not a bad guy.

788
00:40:22,430 --> 00:40:23,380
[Wanted]

789
00:40:25,250 --> 00:40:28,130
I'll split the cost with you.

790
00:40:46,170 --> 00:40:47,290
Have you seen this person?

791
00:40:47,330 --> 00:40:47,990
No.

792
00:40:47,990 --> 00:40:48,030
[Wanted]
No.

793
00:40:48,030 --> 00:40:48,580
[Wanted]

794
00:40:48,580 --> 00:40:49,200
Have you?
[Wanted]

795
00:40:49,200 --> 00:40:50,330
No.
[Wanted]

796
00:40:50,330 --> 00:40:50,370
[Wanted]

797
00:40:52,540 --> 00:40:53,810
Have you seen this person?

798
00:40:54,030 --> 00:40:55,250
No.

799
00:40:59,240 --> 00:41:00,770
What about you? Have you seen her?

800
00:41:00,800 --> 00:41:01,470
Come with me.

801
00:41:01,490 --> 00:41:02,340
No.

802
00:41:16,670 --> 00:41:17,510
What a wasted trip.

803
00:41:17,600 --> 00:41:18,360
Let's go to the next place.

804
00:41:18,380 --> 00:41:19,060
Come with me.

805
00:41:19,300 --> 00:41:23,060
[Tea]

806
00:41:32,030 --> 00:41:32,940
Thank you.

807
00:41:32,980 --> 00:41:33,820
It's nothing.

808
00:41:33,970 --> 00:41:34,680
How do I address you?

809
00:41:34,950 --> 00:41:37,080
My surname is Jin.

810
00:41:37,410 --> 00:41:38,010
Jin?

811
00:41:39,280 --> 00:41:40,160
"Jin", as in to come in?

812
00:41:41,920 --> 00:41:42,710
Jin,

813
00:41:42,730 --> 00:41:43,900
thank you for helping me just now.

814
00:41:44,800 --> 00:41:45,800
I'll treat you to a meal.

815
00:41:48,350 --> 00:41:48,910
Sure.

816
00:41:49,450 --> 00:41:49,940
Let's go.

817
00:41:52,720 --> 00:41:53,280
Jin.

818
00:41:53,310 --> 00:41:54,880
Order whatever you want.

819
00:41:54,900 --> 00:41:55,660
No need.

820
00:41:55,830 --> 00:41:56,790
These two plates are enough.

821
00:41:58,010 --> 00:41:59,070
Just these two?

822
00:42:00,170 --> 00:42:01,050
There are buns over there too.

823
00:42:01,050 --> 00:42:01,850
I'll get them for you.

824
00:42:03,260 --> 00:42:03,910
No need.

825
00:42:04,480 --> 00:42:05,230
No need.

826
00:42:06,350 --> 00:42:06,950
Let's drink.

827
00:42:08,410 --> 00:42:09,730
Cheers.
